11. If I own the trademark, am I guaranteed to get the domain name? Not necessarily. Many Trademarks can exist in many different jurisdictions for the same string depending on use, etc. What we do have however, are multiple abusive registration mechanisms such as 'Rapid Takedown" and Start up Trademark Opposition ("STOP") as well as our IP Protect mechanism to allow IP owners to be notified so they can challenge what they believe may be an infringing registration.
